{"tid":1572162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民陣遊行遭禁 在台港人西門町跨海\"聲\"援","createTime":"2019-09-15T15:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T16:27:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d9c908e480b6d18f157bbedcab8c2592071a50","tid":1572162,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:15:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B2bG-R4gVsZ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2bG-R4gVsZ%2F&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=27c4435b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2bG-R4gVsZ%2F&h=bfc228f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B2bG-R4gVsZ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K4e7BhK-5Qc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK4e7BhK-5Qc&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=a6046e89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K4e7BhK-5Qc</a><br />\n<br />\n香港「民間人權陣線」原訂在今(15)日，在香港再度舉辦反送中遊行，遭到警方發出「反對通知書禁止」，而有一群在台灣的香港人，還是決定一起響應這個活動，他們聚集在台北的西門町，高唱《願榮光歸香港》，不只希望跨海聲援，也希望讓更多人知道香港的處境！<br />\n<br />\n在西門町的街頭，高唱《願榮光歸香港》，一群居住在台灣的香港人，要用歌聲來聲援香港。透過臉書社群，把他們聚集在這裡，活動發起人原本預估只會有2、30人參加，沒想到卻來了超過兩百人！<br />\n<br />\n他們希望用行動跨海聲援「民陣」15日發起的遊行，不僅立法會前議員黃毓民都來參與，但低調堅持不受訪，也有不少來台旅遊的人，特別路過來支持。香港反送中行動，已經持續超過三個月，堅持五大訴求缺一不可，這群香港人，即使人在台灣，還是希望能替故鄉發聲，享受跟台灣一樣的民主自由！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/general/201909/201909151974789.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fcts%2Fgeneral%2F201909%2F201909151974789.html&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=4a896bc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/general/201909/201909151974789.html</a>"},{"pid":"307408f51947a8d9cf226297227ee1e8ef304d57","tid":1572162,"uid":282708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"唔怪得踩場唔見咗毓民，原來過咗嚟台灣"},{"pid":"81f98bc55f14607701b8b9bdc64684df352b4d91","tid":1572162,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"307408f51947a8d9cf226297227ee1e8ef304d57","tid":1572162,"uid":282708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"唔怪得踩場唔見咗毓民，原來過咗嚟台灣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"你個主account 又ban? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349864ce5aeef950b53002e789cf58511a009faf","tid":1572162,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:20:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"8f2b47934c50740311651717e5b1a31579fea048","tid":1572162,"uid":282708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81f98bc55f14607701b8b9bdc64684df352b4d91","tid":1572162,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"307408f51947a8d9cf226297227ee1e8ef304d57","tid":1572162,"uid":282708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"唔怪得踩場唔見咗毓民，原來過咗嚟台灣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"你個主account 又ban? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"無事，另一部機睇緊LIVE"},{"pid":"8ad8b7bd4cd5a0ee45b7393f87b691ceb752f14c","tid":1572162,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"349864ce5aeef950b53002e789cf58511a009faf","tid":1572162,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-